{"tid":508604,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真·第一次成功煎牛扒","createTime":"2017-12-24T12:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T12:54:24.000Z","uid":57346,"like":13,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4056d03d90b160b8521fd4fae6312b7623b49a","tid":508604,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"我本來已經放棄左架喇，不過今日見惠康特價$75兩塊，所以試多最後一次！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次我用最簡單既煮法！將解凍左既牛扒，唔拆原本既真空袋，直接放落熱水（60-70度左右）浸九個字。<br />\n<br />\n之後加黑椒、鹽、橄欖油腌一腌。<br />\n<br />\n放落大火出煙平底鑊，煎一煎兩邊，每邊十零秒有小小燶咁上下。<br />\n<br />\n落牛油、Rose Mary，之後熄火，淋下d汁上面，最後rest 10分鐘，完成！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/195135_df9784511039d268a304db9681ac92e2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F195135_df9784511039d268a304db9681ac92e2.jpeg&h=986b9cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/195141_34e72be89c9dffa14dbd143fb55c1808.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F195141_34e72be89c9dffa14dbd143fb55c1808.jpeg&h=f156a4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/195145_725f85c1deddaaaaf2b4250877ff0716.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F195145_725f85c1deddaaaaf2b4250877ff0716.jpeg&h=1aaf3d24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de604862888619e1b1466f5a85ee45571b23ed27","tid":508604,"uid":114271,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"色都上唔到 邊忽成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490f81e320b7b091be49a1efe59f8060ff0f3205","tid":508604,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"6.5/10"},{"pid":"6563abc6187844e96bdb9c9fcd3b1b1087711ae5","tid":508604,"uid":57346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0